Package: TweetLocViz
Type: Package
Title: Twitter Topic Modeling and Visualization for R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andreas Buchmueller
Maintainer: Andreas Buchmueller <a.buchmueller@stud.uni-goettingen.de>
Description: TweetLocVis enables users to sample geo-located twitter data
    with a regular twitter account. Additionally it comes with abilities for automated
    pre-processing of tweets such as document pooling and a variety of topic models 
    such as LDA and NMF as well as visualizaion capabilities enabling the user a 
    board-range of methods for the analysis and monitoring of public discourse.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/abuchmueller/TweetLocViz
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
